.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
~$*
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak
*.swp
*.swo

# Sync conflict artifacts
*conflicted copy*
*sync-conflict*
*.sync-conflict-*

# Obsidian volatile local state
.obsidian/workspace*.json
.obsidian/cache/
.obsidian/trash/
